txt.en: With Frodo and Bilbo Baggins' birthdays close at hand, Frodo is looking for an adventurer to assist him with a surprise for his uncle Bilbo.  Travel to Rivendell to assist Frodo with his plans.

Frodo can be found in Rivendell, inside The Last Homely House.\n\nThe birthday of Frodo and Bilbo Baggins is upon us!  Frodo is looking for an adventurer to assist him with a birthday surprise for his uncle Bilbo.
'Hello!  Ah, you're here to assist with my birthday surprise for uncle Bilbo?'
Frodo Baggins is looking for an adventurer to help in a birthday surprise for his uncle Bilbo! Travel to Rivendell to find out how you can be of assistance.
Speak to Frodo Baggins in The Last Homely House in Rivendell
Travel to Rivendell and speak with Frodo Baggins
